    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Heavenly Bodies》是一款有关宇航员、身体和失重状态的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款具有挑战性的物理游戏中，探索失重运动不断变化的精妙之处。在一个科研太空站上，用左右摇杆来控制宇航员的手臂，推拉攀爬，探索全实体模拟的场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/c748db6701e9ce9ec42ecd0d9b2dd743.poster.avif?t=1764589319\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/c748db6701e9ce9ec42ecd0d9b2dd743.webm?t=1764589319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/c748db6701e9ce9ec42ecd0d9b2dd743.mp4?t=1764589319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >星空中的职责等待你去完成</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你身负重任，必须让地球上最尖端的工程系统投入运作。能帮你的只有任务指挥部的无线电通讯，而你必须运用敏锐的头脑和灵活的四肢来组装太空望远镜，维护精巧的太阳能电池板，并研究宇宙植物学。不过在失重状态下，一切都不是静止、固定的，任何事都不简单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/33a951d99c081fc63ff8b83e8d616065.poster.avif?t=1764589319\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/33a951d99c081fc63ff8b83e8d616065.webm?t=1764589319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/33a951d99c081fc63ff8b83e8d616065.mp4?t=1764589319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强烈推荐使用控制器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Heavenly Bodies》拥有一套极为独特的移动系统，专门为使用双摇杆控制器而设计。虽然技术上支持可重新绑定的键盘和鼠标控制，但此二者并不能提供所期望的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/4a21498d64906db018900fe03ae02656.poster.avif?t=1764589319\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/4a21498d64906db018900fe03ae02656.webm?t=1764589319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138850/extras/4a21498d64906db018900fe03ae02656.mp4?t=1764589319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众多恒星场景，灵感源于历史上太空探索者和研究人员的壮举。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可单人游玩，或通过本地合作与好友一起玩。你可以单独执行任务，也可搭档太空好友一同探索。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 Steam 的 Remote Play Together 在线游玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在失重状态下，直观地控制宇航员的四肢，以执行具有挑战性的精细操作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操纵极其昂贵的太空载具和精密机械。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70 年代风格的视觉美学，灵感源于太空摄影档案和技术插图。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自定义的控制模式难度和可重新绑定的控制按键。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可重新绑定的控制按键</p></li></ul>",
